{"tid":1837709,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"前線醫護抽生死籌做Dirty team 憂院內冇足夠宿舍自我隔離","createTime":"2020-01-23T17:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T18:03:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f506707ef14c7334131528f887c072eb96b426ad","tid":1837709,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/_VptvnKffsH9VBvmbMlidBiDVFU=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/5L7DZOT5T3O2KIO5LULP2HX3TY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F_VptvnKffsH9VBvmbMlidBiDVFU%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F5L7DZOT5T3O2KIO5LULP2HX3TY.jpg&h=8b37bcc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次Dirty team醫護人員會工作4周後，之後會被調離，再由其他同事接力。<br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒已殺入香港，公立醫院隨時準備要接收大量確診病人。公共醫療醫生協會會長馬仲儀表示，公立醫院有既定機制調配人手，會參考沙士及豬流感時做法，一旦有確診病人，會將前線醫護分為「Dirty team（抗疫隊伍）」及「Clean team（非抗疫隊伍）」，前者專責治理確診病人，後者負責治理一般病人。每次Dirty team醫護人員會工作4周後，之後會被調離，再由其他醫護人員接力。她指部份醫院內科已抽籤，安排誰先做Dirty team，但有醫護擔心院內宿舍不足，做完Dirty team後自我隔離期間沒地方居住。<br />\n<br />\n馬仲儀表示，公立醫院有既定機制，若確診病人再增加時，會將前線醫護會分為Dirty team及Clean team工作，部份醫院內科部門已抽籤安排前線醫護分為不同隊伍，再按屆時實際情況，有需要時擴大Dirty team。若有需要，其他專科護士或專職醫療人員可能要借調到內科Dirty team工作。沙士及豬流感時公立醫院也採用類似做法。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，醫護人員做完4周的Dirty team工作後，會休息2周，其間需自我隔離；但現時不少公立醫院正重建，有醫護人員擔心醫院內沒有足夠宿舍給他們作自我隔離。暫時未知休息兩周期間，是否需要做其他臨床工作。<br />\n<br />\n她指，相信傳染病爆發時，工作壓力較大的是內科、深切治療部、兒科及急症室醫護人員。中高層醫護人員一般都經歷過沙士或豬流感，年輕醫護人員未必經歷過處理疫症，不過醫院對醫護人員都有定期感染控制在職培訓，上周也再加強感染控制培訓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200123/TJHGLZ2O6IM2HZ57XPJ27CCG3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200123%2FTJHGLZ2O6IM2HZ57XPJ27CCG3U%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeK%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=9bba7bbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200123%2FTJHGLZ2O6IM2HZ57XPJ27CCG3U%2F&h=efa09938\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200123/TJHGLZ2O6IM2HZ57XPJ27CCG3U/</a>"},{"pid":"28e1fb184f415299948a31936b100e30f2d893bf","tid":1837709,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:46:00.000Z","msg":"推上去重要野！<br />\n「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7afe282b8f911f595f73ea30b1507620048b04d1","tid":1837709,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:49:19.000Z","msg":"唔罷工真係冇人救到你地呀手足"},{"pid":"45566593319adabfe02792d837f1835e335419cb","tid":1837709,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:02:42.000Z","msg":"頂撚住啊手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3e8c8da9cea0ee7185426b7fe125dbdadb1a56","tid":1837709,"uid":22044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T18:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}